<sect1 id="dir_d4a3144816e2a342522614ea4b514ce1_1autotoc_md86">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::combat</title><para>Combat-related gameplay systems, components, and commands.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d4a3144816e2a342522614ea4b514ce1_1autotoc_md87">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides all building blocks for implementing combat mechanics such as aiming, shooting, and projectile spawning.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d4a3144816e2a342522614ea4b514ce1_1autotoc_md88">
<title>Submodules</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Submodule  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>commands/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Commands for combat actions (ShootCommand, Aim2DCommand)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>components/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Data containers for combat state (aiming direction, cooldowns, projectile config)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>systems/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>ECS systems for processing combat logic (ProjectileSpawnSystem)  </para>
